Home » About
 About Tely


Tely is dedicated to bringing simple high-definition video collaboration to more huddle spaces. Our cloud-optimized endpoints enable creative teams to easily share content and interact more effectively with each other, and with their customers, partners, suppliers through visual collaboration.
Tely was founded in 2010 by Sreekanth and Sudhakar Ravi, successful entrepreneurs with a proven innovation track record at SonicWALL and Code Green Networks. The initial product, Tely HD delivered a Skype video conferencing experience to the living room.
In 2012, Tely received strategic funding from Comcast Ventures and Rogers Venture Partners to accelerate the focus on the business video conferencing market.
Tely’s experienced management team, hail from Avaya, Cisco, Logitech and Polycom. 

Learn more about Tely Labs’ Executive Team





